  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Over the last several decades, occupational stress at workplace comprise a major burden.
      Office based work are more prone to sedentary lifestyle, postural issues, workplace stress,
      repetitive strain injury, poor employee health. Workplace wellness programs has been very
      feasible access to employees at their own convenience and need. Yoga@Work Program was
      developed to suit the need for information technology workers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
