  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Information Technology employee, or trainee willing and able to participate in a
             6-week self-care program during the work day.

          -  Willing to give informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  medical or psychiatric conditions limiting practice of yoga in general

          -  Cognitive impairment
      </textblock>
